cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is about computer vision and machine learning techniques for multiple object tracking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves unsupervised learning, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of clustering and optimization techniques could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the application of the method to pedestrian tracking suggests that it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
